            Visiting our West Campus office (not for shipping)
          Heading link



 
Copy link






Directions: To visit the West Campus office of UIC biomedical engineering, enter  the main entrance to the Medical Sciences Building (MSB) at 835 S. Wolcott Ave. Proceed to the end of the hallway and turn left at wall monitors to room W100, where biomedical engineering staff will direct you to the bioinformatics and imaging areas.
 



